<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">大希地的精调理菲力牛排是已经腌制好的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直接解冻后就可以下锅煎啦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每年各煎2分钟即可~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200819/c7141669b9cc4d35a4f7348b317a6155.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在煎牛排的时候把水烧开</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">放入意面煮熟后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">倒掉多余水分，放入大希地的牛肉意面酱拌匀即可~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">意面团放在盘中，再放入煎好的牛排</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一份高颜值的浪漫牛排意面就做好啦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200819/8cf6e467cdc2468abfc0ff1669176962.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小tips：可以切几个小番茄放入拌好的意面中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再放两片绿色的芹叶装饰一下，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">颜值和level瞬间提升~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200819/62b66193178844c6a4b6ebe61a47fb46.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以再加一句撩人的告白：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鲜美的事物是妙不可言的，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如牛排和你~😘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200819/f3539cf362454a289a929ba2dfc3fae8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">软嫩的菲力牛排</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鲜香可口</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一口下去，从舌头到心头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让人重拾初见时的美好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200819/1684716fbe844438845ac1e789dab8d2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一口牛排一口意面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">味道满分</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱意满分</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200819/2cc86936a53d40dfbadddaecb5af764d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
